{
  "title": "Flavorful Yellow Mediterranean Chicken Skewers",
  "description": "A light and winey Mediterranean dish featuring yellow food colouring, perfect for a crowd, this recipe is sugar-free-friendly and cooked to perfection on a robata-grill.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
  "diet": [
    "sugar-free",
